192 //calculate cost between to reach child node if travelling through parent node
193  double calculate_cost (node* parent_node, node* child_node) //
194  {
195  double cost;
196  if (check_line_obstacle(parent_node->point,child_node->point)) {
197  cost=INFINITY;
198  } else if(parent_node->parent == NULL) {
199  cost=get_dist(parent_node->point,child_node->point);
200  } else {
201  cost=calculate_cost(parent_node->parent,parent_node)+get_dist(parent_node->point,child_node->point);
202  }
203  return(cost);
204  }

292  //function to find closest neighbour to random point
293  node* find_closest(geometry_msgs::Point random_point){
294  if (debugging){
295  ROS_INFO("I've entered find_closest");
296  }
297  int near=0;
298  double temp=0;
299  double mag=INFINITY;
300  double x_diff,y_diff;
301  node* nearest_node=NULL;
302  //ROS_INFO("1random point is (%lf,%lf)",random_point.x,random_point.y);
303  find_neighbours(random_point);
304  for(int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
305  //ROS_INFO("checked neighbours (%.2lf,%.2lf)",neighbours[i]->point.x,neighbours[i]->point.y);
306  x_diff=random_point.x-neighbours[i]->point.x;
307  y_diff=random_point.y-neighbours[i]->point.y;
308  temp=sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2));
309 
310  if(temp<mag){
311  mag=temp;
312  nearest_node=neighbours[i];
313  }
314  }
315  //ROS_INFO("closest node is (%.2lf,%.2lf)",nearest_node->point.x,nearest_node->point.y);
316 
317  return (nearest_node);

320  //function to find neighbours based on grid-based-spacial indexing
321  void find_neighbours(geometry_msgs::Point temp_point){
322  if (debugging){
323  ROS_INFO("I've entered find_neighbours");
324  }
325  int lower_x_grid,upper_x_grid,lower_y_grid,upper_y_grid;
326  path_planning::grid_cell grid=find_grid_cell_for_spatial_indexing(temp_point);
327  //ROS_INFO("test point is (%lf,%lf)",temp_point.x,temp_point.y);
328  //ROS_INFO("grid is (%d,%d)",grid.x,grid.y);
329  neighbours.clear();
330 
331  int search_width=0;
332  while(neighbours.empty()){
333  search_width++;
334  //restrict grid exceeding vector bounds
335  if((grid.x-search_width)<0){
336  lower_x_grid=0;
337  } else {
338  lower_x_grid=grid.x-search_width;
339  }
340  if((grid.x+search_width)>(GRID_WIDTH-1)){
341  upper_x_grid=(GRID_WIDTH-1);
342  } else{
343  upper_x_grid=grid.x+search_width;
344  }
345  if((grid.y-search_width)<0){
346  lower_y_grid=0;
347  } else {
348  lower_y_grid=grid.y-search_width;
349  }
350  if((grid.y+search_width)>(GRID_HEIGHT-1)){
351  upper_y_grid=(GRID_HEIGHT-1);
352  } else {
353  upper_y_grid=grid.y+search_width;
354  }
355  //ROS_INFO("X range (%d,%d)",lower_x_grid,upper_x_grid);
356  //ROS_INFO("Y range (%d,%d)",lower_y_grid,upper_y_grid);
357 
358  for(int i=lower_x_grid;i <= upper_x_grid;i++){
359  for (int j=lower_y_grid;j <=upper_y_grid;j++){
360  //ROS_INFO("Checking grid (%d,%d)",i,j);
361  for(int k=0; k < spatial_grid[i][j].size();k++){
362  //ROS_INFO("spacial_index (%d,%d) point (%lf,%lf)",i,j,spatial_grid[i][j].at(k)->point.x,spatial_grid[i][j].at(k)->point.y);
363  neighbours.push_back(spatial_grid[i][j].at(k));
364  }
365  }
366  }
367  }
368 
369  if (debugging){
370  ROS_INFO("im leaving find neighbour");
371  }
372  }

403  //function to determine if goal is found
404  void is_goal_found(){
405  if (debugging){
406  ROS_INFO("I've entered is goal found");
407  }
408  if (get_dist(root->point,goal) > goal_radius){
409  clear_goal_variables();
410  double x_diff,y_diff,cost_to_goal;
411  find_neighbours(goal);
412  for (int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
413  x_diff=goal.x-neighbours[i]->point.x;
414  y_diff=goal.y-neighbours[i]->point.y;
415  if (abs(x_diff) <= goal_radius && abs(y_diff) <= goal_radius){
416  cost_to_goal=sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2));
417  if(cost_to_goal <= goal_radius && !check_line_obstacle(goal,neighbours[i]->point)){
418  goal_found=true;
419  goal_node=neighbours[i];
420  goal_list.push_back(neighbours[i]);
421  }
422  }
423  }
424  } else {
425  goal_found=false;
426  }
427  if (debugging){
428  ROS_INFO("I've exited is goal found");
429  }
430  return;
431  }

433  //function to find the shortest path to goal
434  std::vector<geometry_msgs::Point> find_path() {
435  if (debugging){
436  ROS_INFO("I've entered find path");
437  }
438  path_cost=get_cost(goal_node)+get_dist(goal_node->point,goal);
439  for (int i=0;i<goal_list.size();i++){
440  if ((get_cost(goal_node)+get_dist(goal_node->point,goal)) > (get_cost(goal_list[i])+get_dist(goal_node->point,goal))){
441  goal_node=goal_list[i];
442  }
443  }
444 
445  if (path_cost > (goal_node->cost + get_dist(goal_node->point,goal))){
446  path_cost=goal_node->cost + get_dist(goal_node->point,goal);
447  geometry_msgs::Point temp_point;
448  path.clear();
449  path_nodes.clear();
450  node* node_ptr = goal_node;
451  temp_point.x=node_ptr->point.x;
452  temp_point.y=node_ptr->point.y;
453  path.push_back(goal);
454  path.push_back(temp_point);
455  path_nodes.push_back(node_ptr);
456  while(node_ptr->parent != NULL)
457  {
458  node_ptr=get_parent(node_ptr);
459  temp_point.x=node_ptr->point.x;
460  temp_point.y=node_ptr->point.y;
461  path.push_back(temp_point);
462  path_nodes.push_back(node_ptr);
463  }
464  }
465  if (debugging){
466  ROS_INFO("I've exited find path");
467  }
468  return(path);
469 
470  }

491  //function to if check line between points is free on map. Based on Bresenham's lins algorithm
492  bool check_line_obstacle (geometry_msgs::Point point_1, geometry_msgs::Point point_2) {
493  /*if (debugging){
494  ROS_INFO("I've entered check line obstacle");
495  }*/
496  geometry_msgs::Point test_point_1,test_point_2;
497  path_planning::grid_cell grid_1,grid_2,grid_1_test,grid_2_test;
498  int difference_x,difference_y;
499  int map_test;
500  double grad, c,x_test,y_test,angle;
501  if(point_1.x > point_2.x){
502  test_point_1=point_2;
503  test_point_2=point_1;
504  }else {
505  test_point_1=point_1;
506  test_point_2=point_2;
507  }
508  grad=(test_point_2.y-test_point_1.y)/(test_point_2.x-test_point_1.x);
509  c=(test_point_2.y-grad*test_point_2.x);
510  angle=atan(grad);
511 
512  grid_1=find_grid_cell(test_point_1);
513  grid_2=find_grid_cell(test_point_2);
514  difference_x=grid_2.x-grid_1.x;
515  difference_y=grid_2.y-grid_1.y;
516  if (test_point_1.x==test_point_2.x){
517  if (difference_y >= 0) {
518  for(int i = grid_1.y+1; i < grid_1.y+difference_y+1; i++) {
519  grid_2_test.x=grid_2.x;
520  grid_1_test.x=grid_1.x;
521  grid_2_test.y=i;
522  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
523  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
524  return(true);
525  }
526  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
527  return(true);
528  }
529  }
530  } else if (difference_y < 0){
531  for(int i = grid_1.y; i > grid_2.y; i--) {
532  grid_2_test.x=grid_2.x;
533  grid_1_test.x=grid_1.x;
534  grid_2_test.y=i;
535  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
536  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
537  return(true);
538  }
539  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
540  return(true);
541  }
542  }
543  }
544  } else if (difference_y >= 0) {
545  if (angle < PI/4){
546  for(int i = grid_1.x+1; i < grid_1.x+difference_x+1; i++) {
547  y_test=(grad*i*map_resolution)+c;
548  grid_2_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
549  grid_1_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
550  grid_2_test.x=i;
551  grid_1_test.x=i-1;
552  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
553  return(true);
554  }
555  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
556  return(true);
557  }
558  }
559  } else {
560  for(int i = grid_1.y+1; i < grid_1.y+difference_y+1; i++) {
561  x_test=((i*map_resolution)-c)/grad;
562  grid_2_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
563  grid_1_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
564  grid_2_test.y=i;
565  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
566  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
567  return(true);
568  }
569  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
570  return(true);
571  }
572  }
573  }
574  } else if (difference_y<0) {
575  if (angle > -PI/4){
576  for(int i = grid_1.x+1; i < grid_1.x+difference_x+1; i++) {
577 
578  y_test=(grad*i*map_resolution)+c;
579  grid_2_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);

592  x_test=((i*map_resolution)-c)/grad;
593  grid_2_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
594  grid_1_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);

624  if (debugging){

626  }
627  path_planning::grid_cell grid=find_grid_cell_for_spatial_indexing(temp_node->point);
628  spatial_grid[grid.x][grid.y].push_back(temp_node);
629  }
630

632  //function to check if node density less that max density
633  bool check_node_density(geometry_msgs::Point new_point){
634  find_neighbours(new_point);
635  if (neighbours.size() > density){
636  return (false);
637  } else {
638  return(true);
639  }
640  }
641 
642  //function to test distance between test point and node to determine if greater than node_dist
643  bool node_dist_check(geometry_msgs::Point test_point, node* closest) {
644  double dist=get_dist(closest->point,test_point);
645  if (dist > node_dist){
646  return(true);
647  } else {
648  return(false);
649  }
650  }
651 
652  double get_dist(geometry_msgs:: Point point_1, geometry_msgs::Point point_2){
653  double x_diff;
654  double y_diff;
655  double dist;
656  x_diff=point_1.x-point_2.x;
657  y_diff=point_1.y-point_2.y;
658  return(sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2)));
659  }

811  geometry_msgs::Point next_point,parent,rand_point;

938  if (path_planning.get_goal_found()){

942  t2 = std::chrono::system_clock::now();
943  time= t2-t1;

945  time_pub.publish(time_to_find_path);

952  for (int i = path_planning.path_length()-2; i >= 0 ;i--){
953  path.points.push_back(path_planning.get_path_point(i));
954  path.points.push_back(path_planning.get_path_point(i+1));
955  marker_pub.publish(path);
956  }
957  //move to next path point if within 0.2 of current one
958  for(int i = path_planning.path_length()-2; i >= 0;){
959  path_pub.publish(path_planning.get_path_point(i));
960  ros::spinOnce();
961  if(path_planning.get_dist(position,path_planning.get_path_point(i)) < 0.2){
962  i--;
963  }
964  }
965  path_pub.publish(path_planning.dummy_point);
966  path.points.clear();
967  line_list.points.clear();
968  points.points.clear();
969  goal_marker.points.clear();
970  path_planning.clear_path_variables();
971  marker_pub.publish(path);
972  marker_pub.publish(points);
973  marker_pub.publish(line_list);
974  marker_pub.publish(goal_marker);
975  path_planning.reset_tree();
976  goal_received=false;
977  t1 = std::chrono::system_clock::now();
978  }
979  }
980  ros::spinOnce();
981  r.sleep();
982  }
983 }
